<br>
Posts which &quot;warn&quot; about someones abuses in game can sometimes serve the public good, but are almost always inflamatory posts which lead to rants and flames. These kinds of posts will not be tolerated on the board. <br>
<br>
If you feel you *must* post a message about someone elses in-game behavior that falls into the categories above (tradescam, ninja looting, etc) then do so on one of many brell rants boards and provide a link. <br>
<br>
Moderators and admins may close or delete posts which have these warnings which do not simply provide a link to an off-board location. If your warning post is deleted, it is with good reason and you should not just turn around and repost it. Reposting of threads which have been deleted may lead to your suspension or banning from this board. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#CC9900>- </font><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bbrellserilis>Brell Serilis</a><font color=#CC9900> - </font><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fbrellserilisfrm48>Town Crier (Rules & Announcements)</a> <font color=#CC9900> - </font><a href="http://www.brellserilis.net">Brell Serilis.net</a><font color=#CC9900> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.3 b4<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  